      This case IS REFERENCED BY (loaded AFTER this record):
        - NO demo tasks - per the seed script's task table, Draft cases
            have NO children in the demo dataset. The dataset
            convention is that children are created only on cases
            that have been picked up by an agent (In Progress and
            beyond, specifically cases 03, 04, 05, 08, 09). This is
            a deliberate dataset design choice that mirrors a realistic
            case lifecycle: tasks (sub-investigations) are typically
            created by the assigned agent during active investigation,
            not by the queue dispatcher at Draft/Open time.
        - NO demo parties - per the seed script's party table, Draft
