        - The avg_time_to_close Manager View single-score widget at
            ../../reports/x_[scope]_avg_time_to_close.xml  (this case
            does NOT contribute because the widget filters on
            status=Closed and this case is Draft, not Closed; only
            cases 06 and 10 contribute to the average)
        - The Agent Workspace's "My Open Cases" list at
            ../../reports/x_[scope]_my_open_cases.xml does NOT include
            this case via its primary filter clause: the list filter
            is "status NOT IN (Resolved, Closed) AND assigned_agent =
            javascript:gs.getUserID()". Draft is NOT in the (Resolved,
            Closed) exclusion set, but assigned_agent is EMPTY on this
            case so the assigned_agent clause does not match the
            current user. The case is therefore NOT in the demo
            agent's "My Open Cases" personal list - which is correct,
            because Draft cases are pre-assignment and have no agent.
            The case is also NOT visible in the case_agent's ACL-
            filtered case list because BOTH "Assigned only" clauses
