            assigned_group is still empty, the
            validate_open_transition subflow MUST throw the form-level
            blocking error (per AAP Section 0.5.5 the condition
            "assigned_group populated" is REQUIRED) and the form
            transition MUST be denied. After assigned_group is manually
            populated on the form (selecting x_[scope]_demo_team), the
