            case 02).
        - The block_draft_backtransition Before-Update business rule
            test in Validation Gate 2 (TRANSITION-BLOCK): this case is
            the canonical "still in Draft" reference state. When an
            operator attempts to set ANY OTHER case's status back to
            Draft (e.g. setting case 02 Open back to Draft via the
            form), the x_[scope]_block_draft_backtransition rule MUST
            surface the verbatim error "Cases cannot be returned to
            Draft." (per AAP Section 0.7.4) and the update MUST be
            aborted. This case demonstrates the legitimate Draft
            terminus for net-new cases; OTHER cases cannot return
            here once they have advanced past Draft.

