    agent prompt's ten authoring rules):

      Rule 1 - Synthetic only (AAP Section 0.7.2 NO-PII clause):
        subject       = "Demo case 01: Draft (General Inquiry)"
                        (verbatim per the agent prompt's required
                        idempotent key)
        description   = "Synthetic Draft case used to verify Draft
                        status visualization and the Draft -> Open
                        transition guard." (verbatim per the agent
                        prompt; the literal `>` is HTML-encoded as
                        `&gt;` per the agent prompt's Rule 10 XML
                        convention; no PII; the wording emphasizes
