                        Draft visualization AND the Draft -> Open
                        transition guard test)
        requester_name  = "Synthetic Requester One" (verbatim per the
                        agent prompt - the explicit "Synthetic" prefix
                        and the ordinal "One" matching this case's
                        position in the dataset eliminate any chance
                        of confusion with a real person; "One" pairs
                        with "Two" through "Ten" on cases 02 - 10 to
                        produce a uniform synthetic identity scheme)
        requester_email = "requester-1@example.invalid" (the .invalid
