      Rule 9 - Idempotency Anchor (folder requirements):
        The case's idempotent key is <subject> =
        "Demo case 01: Draft (General Inquiry)". The companion seed
        script ../../scripts/seed_demo_data.js ensureCase helper
        queries by <subject> before inserting, so re-running the seed
