        action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE" attribute on the inner record
        element ensures the Update Set engine itself is idempotent on
        re-import - if the record already exists by sys_id, the
        engine updates it in place; otherwise it inserts.

      Rule 10 - Scoped Update Set XML Conventions:
        Root element:        <record_update table="x_[scope]_case">
        Inner element:       <x_[scope]_case action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        XML prolog:          <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
        Element ordering:    alphabetical (matching the established
                             sibling convention; cases 02-10 all use
